521
00:40:18,958 --> 00:40:20,751
This is for your drawing tube.

522
00:40:21,419 --> 00:40:22,962
Are you sparing me the hassle?

523
00:40:24,296 --> 00:40:27,133
Put your items on the counter with mine

524
00:40:27,216 --> 00:40:28,634
