full of essential nutrients.

540
00:41:24,899 --> 00:41:26,734
I have no time to set the table.

541
00:41:26,817 --> 00:41:28,110
I have to go to work too.

542
00:41:37,786 --> 00:41:38,787
Where are you?

543
00:41:39,538 --> 00:41:41,832
-Ms. Oh, I'm here.
