-Ms. Oh, I'm here.

546
00:41:52,801 --> 00:41:54,136
Come in.

547
00:41:57,765 --> 00:41:59,391
-Looking for this?
-Gosh.

548
00:41:59,892 --> 00:42:02,394
There you were.
