551
00:42:10,444 --> 00:42:12,404
-Would that be okay?
-Of course.

552
00:42:12,488 --> 00:42:13,489
Come on in.

553
00:42:18,953 --> 00:42:21,330
-Excuse me.
-Don't worry about it.

554
00:42:22,831 --> 00:42:23,666
Check it out.

555
00:42:26,126 --> 00:42:28,379
This is a newly released Blu-ray movie.

556
00:42:28,462 --> 00:42:30,506
