741
00:54:50,245 --> 00:54:51,121
Wait.

742
00:54:55,000 --> 00:54:57,836
Please send it over by Friday.
I'll confirm it.

743
00:54:59,337 --> 00:55:00,255
Goodbye.

744
00:55:18,148 --> 00:55:19,316
KI SEON-GYEOM

745
00:55:19,399 --> 00:55:20,317
He's--

746
00:55:20,817 --> 00:55:24,321
Sell me the new painting at the cafe.
